        <Label VerticalContentAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="571,189,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="175" FontSize="14" FontFamily="Consolas" Height="31" Foreground="White" Grid.Row="1">Made by t0int with â¤</Label>
